{"tid":150203,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 既然有洗閪水，點解唔出返款洗撚水？","createTime":"2017-03-10T00:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T03:07:08.000Z","uid":65071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5a4a9f0ba4e51c804e08160ae8973e14436cfc","tid":150203,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n相信唔少男士都比自己條女屌過條撚臭<br />\n正如男人都屌得多條女個閪臭 <br />\n但臭又要奶咁樣<br />\n既然係咁 我相信洗撚水絕對有佢存在價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要整到成個飛機杯咁撚樣 <br />\n洗撚同時比閪肉包裹住個隻五星級享受<br />\n都咪話唔係聽到都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢款產品一推出市場 相信臭撚男人從此消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗撚水示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zxq3nwv1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzxq3nwv1&h=12c4ce8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"693f4094ece87afd12b5f689f7e82efedf341cdb","tid":150203,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7301098bae7b2a19c19e94e0482c4b1d6fefca","tid":150203,"uid":4072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:21:27.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩"},{"pid":"1ebc39c120580c85ac0a12968b50a64d84af5e79","tid":150203,"uid":16957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚咩</blockquote>我都係想咁講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c25eecaf5c1f8b411475b445b525a8b0bab198","tid":150203,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:24:16.000Z","msg":"洗條撚咩"},{"pid":"0d0ebd4812d96513ed79ad6aad167c35a41f710f","tid":150203,"uid":65071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚咩</blockquote><br />\n洗你就洗 臭你就臭啦 臭撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff00af4abd7fd57d0a786c588a903e93cffea8c0","tid":150203,"uid":36780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:26:11.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解有洗閪水呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為男人放條撚入個閪到洗<br />\n咪有洗閪水既出現囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n送多句比你 洗撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3443b819a93af8c40f6d5dc7173cda0f0b254571","tid":150203,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:39:06.000Z","msg":"原汁原味先正呀"},{"pid":"74ccff3c25b86c879bfdb75dff77d4748a4e2099","tid":150203,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:41:55.000Z","msg":"含啦八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950016687f88e88beaaa1555e3cb7ba4bdddfb30","tid":150203,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T00:50:39.000Z","msg":"洗撚水咩 用閪水洗咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae428b280207c6a83f7deea3c42a209f7659af9","tid":150203,"uid":37281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c768fc0711a8cf52566a59dcf9250e178507d697","tid":150203,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:43:46.000Z","msg":"春水堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4892eed31391a6f623a8f6b6d0a7ef57c9481979","tid":150203,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"洗gap gap"},{"pid":"f16292bdb9650eb3ae37c221cb7ac3db3cf8a69e","tid":150203,"uid":90154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"洗賓周用飛機膠很爽 !<br />\n飛機膠的膠肉有蛋白PVC膠質,用來磨擦賓周可以溶撚走掉袋底老泥好撚乾淨!"},{"pid":"61995cce1ca0990a2bd6eda2de7cf709326b5ed8","tid":150203,"uid":